Madrid were crowned European champions for a 10th time after coming from behind to beat Atletico.

They returned home to a hero's welcome in the early hours and took to the streets of the Spanish capital for an open-top bus parade.

Madrid then invited their fans to the Santiago Bernabeu on Sunday night for a special party to celebrate 'La Decima'.

